text: Isolation is rough. I'm just a lone sole walking the dark. One day I'll be nothing more than what I'm walking through... Empty darkness.

text: Need to press 45's off my chest, not through my head. Keep fighting. Keep going.

author: Alfredo D.
text: (2/2) their presence in your life motivated you to do things again. And you went to bed happy almost every night. Because you know the next morning you'd wake up and they would be there. They saved you without even knowing you needed saving...

author: Alfredo D.
text:
(1/2)You know that feeling where you just want to meet someone all over again. 
You remember the first time talking to them and how exciting it was.
This person was the reason you started to smile again and laugh and look forward to waking up in the morning
To a good morning.
